# Entra Connect Security Module

**Author:** Adrian Johnson (adrian207@gmail.com)  
**Version:** 1.0.0  
**Date:** December 2024

This module provides security features for Entra Connect including PIM, Conditional Access, and Identity Protection.

## Functions

### Set-EntraConnectSecurityBaseline
Applies security baseline configurations.

### Configure-ConditionalAccess
Configures Conditional Access policies.

### Enable-PrivilegedIdentityManagement
Enables and configures PIM.

### Set-IdentityProtectionPolicies
Configures Identity Protection risk policies.

### Enable-MultiFactorAuthentication
Configures MFA requirements.

### Set-EntraConnectAuditLogging
Configures comprehensive audit logging.

### Configure-SecurityDefaults
Applies security default policies.

### Enable-SelfServicePasswordReset
Configures SSPR policies.

### Set-DeviceRegistration
Configures device registration policies.

### Configure-ApplicationProxy
Sets up Application Proxy security.
